title: The Fugitive S02E30 Last Second Of A Big Dream DivX
description:
The Fugitive
S02E30
Last Second of a Big Dream


    * One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
    * Remastered audio and video from VHS TV rip
    * Original music, not a synthesized replacement track!


Airdate: April 20, 1965

Kimble (David Janssen) becomes a pawn of a publicity-hungry showman---who plans to have the fugitive captured at his wild-animal circus.

Craft: Steve Forrest. Fielding: Laurence Naismith. Gerard: Barry Morse. Cartwright: Milton
Selzer.

(Opening segment and credits are missing from this copy of the episode. The program starts with Act 1.)
